    "body" : "<pre><code>int rotation =  getWindowManager().getDefaultDisplay().getRotation();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>this will gives all orientation like normal and reverse</strong></p>\n\n<p>and handle it like </p>\n\n<pre><code>int angle = 0;\nswitch (rotation) {\n    case Surface.ROTATION_90:\n        angle = -90;\n        break;\n    case Surface.ROTATION_180:\n        angle = 180;\n        break;\n    case Surface.ROTATION_270:\n        angle = 90;\n        break;\n    default:\n        angle = 0;\n        break;\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
