    "body" : "<p>if you want to override that onConfigurationChanged method and still want it to do the basic stuff then consider using super.onConfigyrationChanged() as the first statement in the overriden method.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 9344194,
      "reputation" : 505,
      "user_id" : 6935905,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-vTohFobAa_A/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAABI/44janAu_QI8/s256-rj/photo.jpg",
      "display_name" : "DalveerSinghDaiya",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/6935905/dalveersinghdaiya"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
